'''Narayan Athawale''' (1932&ndash;2011) was a leader of [[Shiv Sena]] and a member of [[Lok Sabha]] elected from [[Mumbai]] North Central.<ref>[http://164.100.47.132/LssNew/biodata_1_12/3648.htm Biographical Sketch of Member of XI Lok Sabha<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref> He was a writer and trade unionist. He was also the president of Mumbai [[Marathi language|Marathi]] Patrakar Sangh in 1972.<ref>[http://www.goanews.com/news_disp.php?newsid=1406&catid=222 Goa News | Narayan Athawale no more<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

