{{orphan|date= March 2011}}

'''The Book of the Reason and the Ignorance''' is the first part of the [[Shia]]s oldest [[Oral tradition]] named as 'Osul'i Kafi' or the Principles Sufficient. 

In this book, Kuleini describes the importance of the reason in Shiite belief by traditions narrated by Shiite [[Imam]]s.<ref>اصول کافی.ثقةالاسلام کلینی. the book in Arabic and Persian translation</ref>

